{"tid":1283151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理非同我入嚟] 大家一齊監察政府！！！","createTime":"2019-07-03T17:32:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T17:46:28.000Z","uid":267038,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ae60f7a1f2d155f285e0796509e37dd90e0a47cd","tid":1283151,"uid":267038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T17:32:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">P牌仔和理非第一次開po</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>多謝各位勇武嘅手足<br />\n而且嚟到和理非嘅回合<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">除咗文宣之外<br />\n我哋一齊監察政府</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/government/publication/consultation/current.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fresidents%2Fgovernment%2Fpublication%2Fconsultation%2Fcurrent.htm&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O4eNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=b1fcd6a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/government/publication/consultation/current.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢條link有哂現行開放嘅咨詢<br />\n大大小小大家都俾啲意見佢<br />\n監察政府人人有責</span><br />\n<br />\n主要對象係高階和理非<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">留意返區選條例修訂係7月10日截止咨詢</span></span><br />\n嚟緊區選要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">血債票債</span></span> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">冇可能唔睇下佢想改乜<br />\n有意見大家一齊推爆佢！</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n留意返今次運動緣起係反送中<br />\n仆街政府咨詢得20日<br />\n但係我哋兩日全球登報都趕得起<br />\n20日寫封信 唔好話俾自己聽唔得閒<br />\n<br />\n你可以笑跟政府嗰套玩唔會有用<br />\n唔駛200萬人寫信 我俾你20萬啦<br />\n點都好過得嗰幾千封仲要大部份都撐<br />\n民意基礎呢啲嘢真係唔好懶<br />\n<br />\n個制度係好broken 但嚟到呢個時刻一點一滴都要做<br />\n做得一啲得一啲！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eff8cbc2c2d6745cc4f486b616184dec45b5ece","tid":1283151,"uid":267038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T17:45:57.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講 我要見律師"},{"pid":"9467c77d0eae21d039b3e867532ded512697dd6d","tid":1283151,"uid":267038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T17:46:09.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講 我要見律師"},{"pid":"62c9313aa9ada1ab077a4a444acd6f230d51fc66","tid":1283151,"uid":267038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T17:46:28.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講 我要見律師"}]}